INSTALLATION of Battles of Antargis
===================================

On Ubuntu ( Debian ? )
----------------------

First install some dependencies:

> sudo apt-get install g++ libsdl1.2-dev libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-mixer1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libpng-dev cmake libgl-dev libboost-dev libboost-test1.74-dev libglm-dev

continue with 'Linux'

Linux
-----

Then compile the game using debug-symbols - as it is in active development

> ./makeDebug.sh

Then run the game:

> ./Debug/antargis
